'''Lisa Shaunessy''' was Publicity Assistant during filming of [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']] in Sydney.

She appeared as a cameo in ''Revenge of the Sith'' portraying [[Silya Shessaun]], but the character did not feature in the final release of the film.

